tr.td: <Settings DefaultValue="true" Type="Boolean" Name="AH Items" Summary="If set to true this profile will sell items on AH, otherwise it'll mail items to an alt.If mailing items to alt make sure to set the Grind Bot's 'Recipient' field to your alts name." Category="Profile" Global="False" Hidden="False" />
<Settings DefaultValue="true" Type="Boolean" Name="Herb" Summary="Set to true if you want to level herbalism" Category="Profile" Global="False" Hidden="False" />
<Settings DefaultValue="true" Type="Boolean" Name="Mining" Summary="Set to true if you want to level Mining" Category="Profile" Global="False" Hidden="False" />

<CustomAction Code="if (((bool)Settings["Mining"] &&
 (MiningLevel == MiningMaxLevel || ((bool)Settings["Herb"] && MiningMaxLevel > HerbMaxLevel ))) ||
 !(bool)Settings["Mining"])
{
 mining = Bots.Gatherbuddy.GatherbuddySettings.Instance.GatherMinerals = false;
}" />

<CustomAction Code="if ((bool)Settings["Mining"] && MiningLevel != MiningMaxLevel && 
 ( MiningMaxLevel <= HerbMaxLevel || !(bool)Settings["Herb"] ))
{
 mining = Bots.Gatherbuddy.GatherbuddySettings.Instance.GatherMinerals = true;
}" />

<CustomAction Code="if (((bool)Settings["Herb"] && (HerbLevel == HerbMaxLevel || ((bool)Settings["Mining"] && HerbMaxLevel > MiningMaxLevel))) || !(bool)Settings["Herb"]) herb = Bots.Gatherbuddy.GatherbuddySettings.Instance.GatherHerbs = false;" />
<!--enable Herb in GB2 if enabled in profile Settings and Herb MaxLevel <= Mining.MaxLevel-->

<CustomAction Code="if ((bool)Settings["Herb"] && HerbLevel != HerbMaxLevel &&
 (HerbMaxLevel <= MiningMaxLevel || !(bool)Settings["Mining"] ) )
{
 herb = Bots.Gatherbuddy.GatherbuddySettings.Instance.GatherHerbs = true;
}" />
<CustomAction Code="MessageBox.Show("Please switch to Eastern Kingdoms continent");" />
